        {
            "id": "http://silentlight.tk/2021/03/22/JavaScript%E5%9F%BA%E7%A1%80%E7%AC%94%E8%AE%B0/",
            "url": "http://silentlight.tk/2021/03/22/JavaScript%E5%9F%BA%E7%A1%80%E7%AC%94%E8%AE%B0/",
            "title": "JavaScript基础笔记",
            "date_published": "2021-03-22T11:23:00.000Z",
            "content_html": "<h2 id=\"JavaScript简介\"><a href=\"#JavaScript简介\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"JavaScript简介\"></a>JavaScript简介</h2><p>1.什么是JavaScript</p>\n<blockquote>\n<p>JavaScript 是一门跨平台、面向对象的脚本语言，它能使网页可交互（例如拥有复杂的动画，可点击的按钮，通俗的菜单等）。</p>\n</blockquote>\n<p>2.JavaScript的构成</p>\n<ul>\n<li>ECMAScript（JavaScript标准）</li>\n<li>DOM</li>\n<li>BOM</li>\n</ul>\n<p>3.JS的特点</p>\n<ul>\n<li>解释型语言</li>\n<li>类似于C、Java的语法结构</li>\n<li>动态语言</li>\n<li>基于原型的面向对象</li>\n</ul>\n<p>4.JavaScript中的hello world</p>\n<figure class=\"highlight javascript\"><table><tr><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">&lt;script&gt;</span><br><span class=\"line\">        <span class=\"comment\">/* </span></span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"comment\">        下面三条语句顺序执行</span></span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"comment\">         */</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">        alert(<span class=\"string\">&quot;Hello World!&quot;</span>);</span><br><span class=\"line\">        <span class=\"comment\">// 可以在body中输出一段内容</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">        <span class=\"built_in\">document</span>.write(<span class=\"string\">&quot;Hello World!&quot;</span>);</span><br><span class=\"line\">        <span class=\"comment\">//向控制台输出内容</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">        <span class=\"built_in\">console</span>.log(<span class=\"string\">&quot;Hello World!&quot;</span>);</span><br><span class=\"line\">    &lt;/script&gt;</span><br><span class=\"line\">&lt;/head&gt;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n\n<p>5.JS编写位置</p>\n<p>写在标签里，缺点是结构和行为相耦合，不方便维护</p>\n<p>例如写在标签的onclick属性中</p>\n<figure class=\"highlight html\"><table><tr><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"tag\">&lt;<span class=\"name\">button</span> <span class=\"attr\">onclick</span>=<span class=\"string\">&quot;alert(&#x27;Hello World!&#x27;);&quot;</span>&gt;</span><span class=\"tag\">&lt;/<span class=\"name\">button</span>&gt;</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n\n<p>写在链接的href属性中</p>\n<figure class=\"highlight html\"><table><tr><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"tag\">&lt;<span class=\"name\">a</span> <span class=\"attr\">href</span>=<span class=\"string\">&quot;javascript:alert(&#x27;Hello World!&#x27;);&quot;</span>&gt;</span><span class=\"tag\">&lt;/<span class=\"name\">a</span>&gt;</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n\n\n\n<p>写在内部script标签里</p>\n<p>外部js文件引入</p>\n<p>script标签一旦用于引入外部文件了，就不能编写代码了，即使编写浏览器也会忽略</p>\n<p>JS基本语法</p>\n<p>注释，与Java的相同。</p>\n",
            "tags": [
                "学习笔记"
            ]
        },
